Package: MRAinla
Type: Package
Title: INLA-MRA: An algorithm for large spatiotemporal datasets
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Luc Villandre
Maintainer: Luc Villandre <luc.villandre@hec.ca>
Description: The package fits the INLA-MRA approach proposed by Villandre et al., best suited for spatiotemporal datasets of sizes under 1.5 million observations. It uses an importance sampling algorithm to produce posteriors for model parameters and hyperparameters.
